               throws KeycloakUserAlreadyExistsException,

                      KeycloakUnknownErrorException
        Method creates a new customer. It also creates the related keycloak user.
        Parameters:
        customerEntity - new customer
        Throws:
        KeycloakUserAlreadyExistsException - if the keycloak user already exists
        KeycloakUserIsNotAuthorizedException - if the keycloak admin user is not authorized
        CustomerAlreadyExistsException - if the customer already exists
        KeycloakEndpointNotFoundException - if the keycloak rest endpoints are not found
        KeycloakUnknownErrorException - if any other keycloak error occurs
